<HEADLINE> Four Argentine Soccer Clubs Stand in World's Top 100 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BUENOS AIRES, August 6 (Xinhua) -- A total of five Argentine
soccer clubs joined the ranks of the World Top 100 of the Month in
July, with the newly-crowned Libertadores Cup champion River Plate
at the fifth place, reports reaching here said on Tuesday.
</P>
