over Colombia's America de Cali on June 26, was also fifth in June.
</P>
<P>
In July's rankings, Spain's FC Barcelona finished first while
Dutch team Ajax was second. The third and fourth places went to
Germany's Bayern Munich and Italy's AC Milan respectively.
