issued by the Motherland Party, Democratic Left Party, Republican
People's Party, Grand Unity Party and National Action Party in
opposition to Erbakan's indirect dialogue with the PKK, which has
been fighting a 12-year guerrilla war for self-rule in
southeastern Turkey. 
