<HEADLINE> Book on China's Aviation History to Be published </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, August 7 (Xinhua) -- China's first book about the
country's aviation history will be published soon, according to a
report in the "People's Daily."
</P>
<P>
Twenty five authors and editors from different fields in the
air force, civil aviation and the aviation industry as well as
other departments have been compiling the book for six years, the
newspaper report said.
