<HEADLINE> Czech Republic, St. Lucia Set Up Diplomatic Ties </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PRAGUE, August 6 (Xinhua) -- The Czech Republic and St. Lucia
established formal diplomatic relations today, the Czech News
Agency reported.
</P>
<P>
